item.title: Can someone help me portforward and the rest?
item.dc:creator: @O_M_G1 O M G
item.description:
@O_M_G1 wrote:

Press Custom Service

Make the application name the name of your server

Make the port the port of your server (should be 43594 or 5555)

Enable it

Put your Gateway IP in the IP box at the end.

Save.
